			  </div>
				<div class="r main about lineheight30px">			    <br />
				  LEONESSAbrevini is a joint venture that was established between the Italian-based La Leonessa S.p.A. and the Brevini Power Transmission S.p.A. in 2011. The mission of the company located in Yancheng, in Jiangsu province, is to offer to Chinese customer high quality slewing bearings and possibly a combination of planetary gearboxes and slewing bearings as an integrated package solution, for many different equipment applications like water treatment plants, thruster and wind mills. <br />
<br />

Leonessabrevini slewing bearings are designed and manufactured according to Leonessa S.p.A. know how accumulated in more than 40 years of slewing bearings manufacturing in Italy. The JV with Brevini offers the possibility to the customers to have from one supplier the integrated package of slewing bearing and planetary gearbox, that is guaranteeing the best performance and maximum reliability of both components.<br />
<br />

Through their global experience, Leonessabrevini already knows what is important for customers, by offering a more integrated product it is possible to avoid many mechanical problems, it is an important element that participate to the success of customers company; moreover purchasing an integrated product is synonymous of less costs because of the high level of efficiency and effectiveness, these can be seen for examples in faster delivery, one direct and fast communication, that in a fast growing market it leads to a hard to imitate competitive advantage among competitors. Furthermore customers want a supplier to provide them all critical components that has been throughly analyzed and custom designed to achieve top performance and maximum reliability.<br />
<br />

La Leonessa S.p.A. is a company established in Italy in 1970 to produce slewing rings primarily for the construction equipment market; the company has expanded its business worldwide and achieved a dominant position in several market segments. In accordance to the new emerging sensibility among environmental issues, in 2005 La Leonessa S.p.A. started producing slewing bearings for the wind turbine market that it is in a strong expansion phase. Flexibility , quality and customer care are the keywords to describe the company, it can satisfy almost any request from their customers. Since 1970 La Leonessa S.p.A.has designed and produced more than 4,000 different slewing bearing’s models. This flexibility melted with professionalism and innovation on both process and product gave the opportunity to the company to face head high the economic crisis in the European market.<br />
<br />

Brevini Power Transmission S.p.A. is a company founded in 1960 in Reggio Emilia, Italy; Nowadays the company is one of the top ten manufacturers of planetary gearboxes and mechanical transmission for industrial applications, mobile machines and wind generators. Since its foundation the company pursued through technology innovation the best price/performance ratio without undermining the quality of the final product even in the most extreme conditions. One of the most important strengths that Brevini has brought to Leonessabrevini is its worldwide distribution network developed during the years since its foundation. The last 10 years have been years of enormous growth for the company: from a scenario of 470 employees to 1200 that are employed today in its factories in Italy, China, Germany and USA; the production raised from 67,000 to 172,000 gearboxes per annum .
